    "body" : "<p>I don't recall of a \"indexOf\" on arrays other than coding it for yourself... though you could probably use one of the many <code>java.util.Arrays#binarySearch(...)</code> methods (see the <a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/1.5.0/docs/api/java/util/Arrays.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Arrays javadoc</a>) if your array contains primitive types</p>\n"
