    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>The List interface has an indexOf() method, and you can obtain a List from your array with Array's asList() method. Other than that, Array itself has no such method. It does have a binarySearch() method for sorted arrays.</p>\n"
