      "body" : "-1: First this mutates the original array to be sorted which we may not want. Second it gives the answer wrt the sorted array, not the original array which is likely what we want (if we wanted the answer wrt sorted array, it would already be sorted). Third since sorting is O(n log n) this is slower than just going through the array linearly. So this answer is both wrong and inefficient."
